Package: btglm
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-6-15
title: Bayesian threshold generalized linear models
Description: This package fits distributed lag models (DLMs) to describe
  how the association between the presence of built environment features
  and an outcome varies as a function of distance between locations for
  study participants and locations for environment features.
Author: Andrew Whiteman <awhitem@umich.edu>,
	Jian Kang <jiankang@umich.edu>
Maintainer: Andrew Whiteman <awhitem@umich.edu>
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2),
	 coda,
	 foreach,
	 glmnet,
	 iterators,
	 methods,
	 Rcpp (>= 0.12.17),
	 RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.4.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp,
	   RcppEigen
Imports: coda,
	 foreach,
	 glmnet,
	 iterators
Suggests: devtools,
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
